<h1 id="toc0"><span>RESULTS</span></h1>
<h1 id="toc1"><span>Congratulations to our winners, <span style="color: gold"><strong>Nobody's Winning,</strong></span> who secured a final score of 377 upvotes across their top five entries!</span></h1>
<h1 id="toc2"><span>And to our runners-up, <span style="color: silver"><strong>Mikasa Junior</strong></span> and the bronze medalists <span style="color: goldenrod"><strong>Resurrecting Resurrection</strong></span>!</span></h1>
<h2 id="toc3"><span>And thank you to everyone that contributed to or participated in this contest - you made this possible.</span></h2>
<div class="collapsible-block">
